item.title: Super Rare Trade
item.content:encoded:
I'm in the same position Omnifox was in, a few weeks ago. I have an extra Necklace that I would like to trade to someone. Like Omni, I am in need of K-Dog's Headband, but I will entertain other offers.

Please post in this thread if you would consider a trade.
